Gemini
Fixing Dependency Conflicts and Bloat
Enterprise logo
Conversation with Gemini
Please fix any dependecy conflicts in this file

This package.json is an absolute unit—it looks like the "everything bagel" of npm!

The primary, direct conflict in your file is that debug is declared in both dependencies and devDependencies with different versions. npm does not allow a package to be in both places simultaneously and will flag this as an issue.

To fix the structural conflict, I have removed the older version (^4.1.1) from devDependencies and kept the newer version (^4.3.4) in dependencies.

